    <!-- Tips -->
    <string name="tip">Tips:</string>
    <string-array name="tips">
        <item>!• When Shizuku is not ready, only System Info is shown; once ready, the SIM list auto-refreshes and the primary SIM is selected by default.</item>
        <item>• After Shizuku is ready, current system configuration is loaded automatically into switches and inputs.</item>
        <item>• Configuration applies to the selected SIM card; choosing \"All SIM\" applies in batch.</item>
        <item>• After a successful reset, current system state is synced automatically.</item>
        <item>• If you have signal but no data, check whether Access Point Name (APN) is empty after system updates.</item>
    </string-array>

